msgid "Unresolved questions"
msgstr ""

#: src/0201-error-chaining.md:284
msgid "Conventions"
msgstr ""

#: src/0201-error-chaining.md:286
msgid ""
"This RFC does not define any particular conventions around cause chaining or "
"concrete error types. It will likely take some time and experience using the "
"proposed infrastructure before we can settle these conventions."
msgstr ""

